data.description: Searching for stunning views that go on for days? Peaceful, private property that is still close enough to town to enjoy all the conveniences you crave? Would you love the flexibility of an attached guest house that you could also be used as an AirB&B? This gorgeous home checks all the boxes and is such a rare find. Enter on the main floor to soaring ceilings, a breathtaking view, tons of natural light and impressive architectural details. Primary bedroom is on the main floor with full ensuite bath, dual vanities and dual walk-in closets. Kitchen opens to dining and family room for easy entertaining that can easily spill out to the upper balcony. Upstairs you’ll find two generously sized bedrooms and an open study area between. Downstairs, the fully finished walk-out basement serves as perfect guest quarters or STR. Full kitchen, living, bedroom and bath with laundry facilities and a private deck. Beautiful travertine tile, hardwood, and stained concrete flooring – no carpet. All appliances convey making this truly turn-key. The back yard slopes to a wet-weather creek and walking path along property line up the hill. Enjoy back yard bonfires and friendly game of disc golf. Covered parking pad for a boat or camper at the front of the property. No HOA and ETJ offers maximum flexibility for homeowners. Convenient to Lake Travis recreation areas and marinas.
